title: Apple iPhone 6s, iPhone 6s Plus goes up for pre-order
text: It’s that time of the year when Apple fans sit awake at midnight, in front of their computers, just to make an effort to pre-order the latest iPhones. Yes, pre-orders for the new iPhone 6s and iPhone 6s Plus went live in the United States, Canada, China, France, Germany, Hong Kong, Japan, New Zealand , Puerto Rico, Singapore, Australia, and the UK. Some enthusiastic iPhone fans who were successful in placing their orders have taken it to Twitter to express their joy. I HAVE EXCHANGED MONEY FOR THE PROMISE OF A SMALL LUMP OF GLASS AND METAL.
